      <td>Monday 20 July 2020</td>
      <td>Civil work from <a rel="external" href="https://courttribunalfinder.service.gov.uk/courts/worthing-county-court-and-family-court" class="govuk-link">Worthing County Court</a> and family work from <a rel="external" href="https://courttribunalfinder.service.gov.uk/courts/worthing-county-court-and-family-court" class="govuk-link">Worthing Family Court</a>
</td>
    </tr>
